OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773159075
OL,3,CWoman 'pulled own baby out' whilst
OL,4,Cwaiting for maternity care
OL,6,FA woman has described 'pulling her own
OL,7,Fbaby out' as she waited for maternity
OL,8,Fcare to arrive at her home.
OL,10,FGemma Lisi, 34, from Stranraer, says
OL,11,Fshe was left in "panic mode" after
OL,12,Fbeing told that the support she needed
OL,13,Fwas travelling from elsewhere in
OL,14,FDumfries and Galloway.
OL,16,FShe later gave birth to her son,
OL,17,FCarlo, in a birth pool at home with
OL,18,Fonly her husband by her side.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
