FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773159075
OL,3,CWoman 'pulled own baby out' whilst
OL,4,Cwaiting for maternity care
OL,6,FFollowing the ordeal, Gemma waited
OL,7,Fanother forty minutes before a midwife
OL,8,Feventually got to her.
OL,10,FRecalling her experience, Gemma said:
OL,11,F"I had a little panic and I thought
OL,12,F'I'm just going to jump in the pool'.
OL,13,FI was able to catch him and I pulled
OL,14,Fhim up to my chest.
OL,16,F"I was able to kind of sit there until
OL,17,Fthe midwives came. But it was about
OL,18,Fforty minutes after I'd given birth
OL,19,Fthat they arrived.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773159075
OL,3,CWoman 'pulled own baby out' whilst
OL,4,Cwaiting for maternity care
OL,6,F"They came and they were great. They
OL,7,Fwere lovely women and they did a great
OL,8,Fjob when they got there. But it could
OL,9,Fhave been completely different. Any
OL,10,Fcomplication could have arisen.
OL,12,F"It's definitely something that I feel
OL,13,Fneeds to be addressed."
OL,15,FWomen with low-risk pregnancies were
OL,16,Fable to give birth at Galloway
OL,17,FCommunity Hospital in Stranraer until
OL,18,F2018 when the maternity unit there
OL,19,Fclosed due to staffing issues.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773159075
OL,3,CWoman 'pulled own baby out' whilst
OL,4,Cwaiting for maternity care
OL,6,FIt means that pregnant mothers living
OL,7,Fin and around the town now have to
OL,8,Ftravel more than seventy miles to
OL,9,FDumfries for their babies to be
OL,10,Fdelivered.
OL,12,FIn 2024 there was the option to reopen
OL,13,Fthe unit in Stranraer, but at the time
OL,14,Fthis was rejected by the health board,
OL,15,Fwhich said it wouldn't be the best use
OL,16,Fof resources.
OL,18,FGemma told ITV Border the reason she
OL,19,Fwanted to have a home delivery was to
OL,20,Favoid that long journey.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773159075
OL,3,CWoman 'pulled own baby out' whilst
OL,4,Cwaiting for maternity care
OL,6,FAngela Armstrong, who campaigns on
OL,7,Fhealth issues in the local area, said:
OL,8,F"I cannot believe that in this day and
OL,9,Fage, such a thing could possibly
OL,10,Fhappen.
OL,12,F"That must have been so scary for
OL,13,FGemma. We're told that there are
OL,14,Fmidwives in the area. (But) the
OL,15,Fjourneys around here take a long, long
OL,16,Ftime. Roads are bad, which they often
OL,17,Fare.
OL,19,FShe added: "I wish I could say
OL,20,Feverything is fine. I would be lying."
OL,26,@vD@WpmvD@[pn
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/10
