CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773159075
OL,3,CWoman 'pulled own baby out' whilst
OL,4,Cwaiting for maternity care
OL,6,FNHS Dumfries and Galloway said it
OL,7,Fcannot comment on individual cases but
OL,8,Fstressed that the welfare of mothers
OL,9,Fand children is the primary concern of
OL,10,Fthe midwifery team.
OL,12,FDumfries and Galloway is one of the
OL,13,Fmost rural areas in Scotland, with
OL,14,Fseveral remote communities, including
OL,15,Fin and around Stranraer.
OL,17,FThe health board notes that geography
OL,18,Fcan influence response times, and it
OL,19,Fsays it works closely with each
OL,20,Fpregnant woman to plan appropriately.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773159075
OL,3,CWoman 'pulled own baby out' whilst
OL,4,Cwaiting for maternity care
OL,6,FIn a statement a spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Babies can sometimes arrive very
OL,8,Fquickly, particularly where this is
OL,9,Fnot a first pregnancy. This is
OL,10,Fsomething we discuss with all women,
OL,11,Fincluding those planning a hospital
OL,12,Fbirth and those requesting a home
OL,13,Fbirth.
OL,15,F"As part of routine antenatal care, a
OL,16,Ffull risk assessment is undertaken to
OL,17,Fconsider individual circumstances and
OL,18,Fto support informed decision-making
OL,19,Fabout place of birth.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773159075
OL,3,CWoman 'pulled own baby out' whilst
OL,4,Cwaiting for maternity care
OL,6,F"Midwives attend as soon as possible
OL,7,Fwhen contacted; however, in some cases
OL,8,Flabour progresses so quickly that a
OL,9,Fbaby is born before a midwife arrives.
OL,10,FOur midwives live and work across
OL,11,FDumfries and Galloway, including in
OL,12,Fsome of the region's most rural and
OL,13,Fremote communities, and home birth
OL,14,Fcare is provided through an on-call
OL,15,Frota system. The attending midwife
OL,16,Fwill therefore depend on who is on
OL,17,Fcall at the time labour begins.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1773159075
OL,3,CWoman 'pulled own baby out' whilst
OL,4,Cwaiting for maternity care
OL,6,F"We encourage women to make early
OL,7,Fcontact at the onset of labour.
OL,8,FHowever, labour can sometimes progress
OL,9,Fextremely rapidly, particularly
OL,10,Ffollowing previous pregnancies, and
OL,11,Fthe time required for a midwife to
OL,12,Freach someone can vary depending on
OL,13,Flocation and travel distance."
OL,15,FIt added: "Births Before Arrival do
OL,16,Foccur across Scotland, even with
OL,17,Fcareful planning in place. While they
OL,18,Fremain uncommon, every case is
OL,19,Freviewed to understand what worked
OL,20,Fwell and where further improvements
OL,21,Fcan be made."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/10
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
